RECORDED FOR FINANCIAL MANAGEMENT SRVCS
NOTICE OF MECHANIC'S LIEN
CUTTING EDGE SAWING & DRILLING, 1208 EAST 8725 SOUTH, SANDY, UT 84094,
lien claimant, acting through it's duly authorized agent, Financial Management
Services, L.L.C ., hereby holds and claims a mechanic's lien, pursuant to Section
38-1-1 et. seq. Utah Code Annotated 1953, as amended, upon the property and
improvements thereon owned or reputed to be owned by DONALD M & JULIA EADES and
located at approximately 352 EAST RIVERMEADOWS DRIVE, ALPINE, UTAH County, Utah,
more particularly as follows:
LEGAL: LOT 10, RIVERMEADOWS ESTATES, PLAT C, PARCEL # 51-217-010
The lien claimant claims and holds a lien upon the above described
property for amounts owing for furnishing CONCRETE CUTTING upon or in connection
with the improvement of said real property. The lien claimant was employed by
PROSPECTOR ONE, 37 EAST 800 NORTH, OREM, UT 84057 or furnished the aforesaid
CONCRETE CUTTING to said company. There is due and owing to lien claimant the sum
of $287.00 PRINCIPAL INCLUDING LIEN FILING FEES for the CONCRETE CUTTING it
furnished, together with interest, costs and attorney's fees.
CUTTING EDGE SAWING & DRILLING furnished the first said CONCRETE CUTTING
=
on AUGUST 18, 1997, and the last CONCRETE CUTTING were furnished on AUGUST 18,
1997.
Dated this 24 October, 1997.
CUTTING EDGE SAWING & DRILLING, claimant
By agent, Financial Management Services, L.L.C.
